text: Voiceless may refer to: *Voicelessness, linguistic sounds produced without vibrating the larynx *Muteness, the property of being unable to produce a voice *Aphasia, the condition of being unable to speak *A lack of power (social and political) *Voiceless (animal welfare group), the animal protection institute based in Sydney, Australia *Voiceless (film), a 2016 American film ==See also== *Speechless (disambiguation)
title: Voiceless (disambiguation)
